high_descs: Turn around, go toward the stool, turn right, and go to the small sink.
Take the butter knife from in front of the small sink.
Turn around, turn around, and go to the small sink.
Put the knife in the small sink, turn on the water, turn off the water, and take the knife from the sink.
Turn right, go to the large sink, and turn left.
Put the knife in the large sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean knife in the large sink.

high_descs: Turn left and walk up to the kitchen sink
Pick up the butter knife from the sink
Turn right and then face back toward the sink
Wash the knife under water in the sink then remove it
Turn right then face back toward the sink
Put the knife down on the edge of the counter in front of the sink
anns.task_desc: Put the washed knife on the kitchen counter

high_descs: Go left and stand to face the sink.
Pick the knife up out of the sink.
Move to the right a bit and face the sink again.
Put the knife in the sink and turn the water on and then off and pick the knife up again.
Move to the right edge of the sink.
Put the knife down in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean knife in the sink.
